actual.comment:
1. The Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) developed and communicated an Election Road Map/calendar for the 2015 elections with key stakeholders;
2. Staff of targeted INEC departments trained on electoral processes and procedures in accordance with timelines set in the Strategic Programme of Action 2012-2016;
3. The Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) gender policy developed; 
4. Zonal level Civil Society Organizations (CSOs) undertook voter education and election observation services for Ekiti and Osun State elections; Civil Society Organizations (CSOs) roster updated in the 6 geo-political zones and framework developed to implement voter education at zonal levels; 
5. A Nigerian media Code of Election Coverage developed and adopted by key stakeholders in December 2014.

